return ['messages'=>['<h3>Want to see what\'s new? <br>Head to JCK and explore our latest collection!</h3>'=>'<h3>想瞭解新增功能？  <br>前往 JCK 探索我們的最新系列！</h3>','<h5>Consistent quality</h5>
<p>CNC technology consistently yields high-quality products with the same level of precision manufacturing.</p>'=>'<h5>始終如一的品質</h5>
<p>CNC 技術始終如一地生產出具有相同精密製造水準的高品質產品。</p>','<h5>Greater precision</h5>
<p>CNC technology ensures that each piece meets your specifications exactly, reducing the likelihood of errors or rework.</p>'=>'<h5>更高的精度</h5>
<p>CNC 技術確保每件產品都完全符合您的規格，從而減少出錯或返工的可能性。</p>','<h5>Increased design flexibility</h5>
<p>CNC technology allows us to create custom pieces that are truly unique and personalized while meeting stringent deadlines.</p>'=>'<h5>提高設計靈活性</h5>
<p>CNC 技術使我們能夠創建真正獨特和個人化的定製作品，同時滿足嚴格的截止日期。</p>','<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>2</strong></span></big></p>
<p>Improved efficiency and productivity in the manufacturing process, enhancing the ability to meet customer demand in a timely and cost-effective manner. </p>'=>'<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>2</strong></span></big></p>
<p>提高製造流程的效率和生產力，增強及時且經濟高效地滿足客戶需求的能力。  </p>','<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>3</strong></span></big></p>
<p>Ability to create custom pieces more easily and with greater accuracy, giving us a competitive edge in the market, and better fulfilling our customers’ needs.</p>'=>'<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>3</strong></span></big></p>
<p>能夠更輕鬆、更準確地創建定製件，使我們在市場上具有競爭優勢，並更好地滿足客戶的需求。</p>','<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent">CNC technology</span></big> allows for the creation of precise and complex shapes and designs out of metal. It stands for "Computer Numerical Control". <span class="trx_addons_inverse">Think of it as a robot that follows a set of programmed instructions to make something very small and detailed.</span> In the jewellery industry, CNC machines can be used to create a wide range of jewellery pieces, from simple wedding bands to intricate, multi-layered designs. As a bespoke manufacturing jeweller, CNC technology acts as a powerful complement – not a replacement – to our decades of experience and craftsmanship. It provides our masters with a new range of tools for jewellery production.</p>'=>'<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent">CNC 技術</span></big> 允許用金屬創建精確和複雜的形狀和設計。 它代表“Computer Numerical Control”。  <span class="trx_addons_inverse">可以把它想像成一個機器人，它遵循一組程式設計指令來製作非常小和詳細的東西。</span>  在珠寶行業，CNC 機器可用於製作各種珠寶作品，從簡單的結婚戒指到複雜的多層設計。 作為一家定製製造珠寶商，CNC 技術是我們數十年經驗和工藝的有力補充，而不是替代品。 它為我們的大師提供了一系列新的珠寶生產工具。</p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong><big>1</big></strong></span></p>
<p>Greater precision and accuracy in the creation of jewellery pieces, especially for intricate filigree work or small pave-set stones.</p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong><big>1</big></strong></span></p>
<p>在珠寶作品的創作中，尤其是複雜的金銀絲作品或密鑲小寶石時，精度和準確性更高。</p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">The contrasting shades of yellow and white gold intertwine harmoniously, creating a captivating interplay of colors. </span></p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">黃金和白金的對比色調和諧地交織在一起，營造出迷人的色彩交織。  </span></p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">The smoothness of the cuts and the crispness of the edges highlight the attention to detail and artistry that went into creating this <small>stunning</small> piece.</span></p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">切割的光滑度和邊緣的清脆度突出了對細節和藝術的關注，這些都是創造這件 <small>令人驚歎的</small> 作品的動力。</span></p>','<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">Date &amp; Time</span></strong><br /><span class="trx_addons_accent">2-4 Jun (Fri-Sun) 0930-1800</span><br /><span class="trx_addons_accent">5 Jun (Mon) 0930-1630</span></p><p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">Booth 53107, Level 1, Hong Kong Pavilion<br /></span></strong><strong style="font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); color: var(--theme-color-text); letter-spacing: 0px;"><span class="trx_addons_accent">The Venetian Expo, Las Vegas, Nevada</span></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">日期 &amp; 時間</span></strong><br><span class="trx_addons_accent">6月2日至4日（週五至周日） 0930-1800</span><br><span class="trx_addons_accent">6 月 5 日 （星期一） 0930-1630</span></p><p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">香港館 1 樓 53107 展位<br></span></strong><strong style="font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); color: var(--theme-color-text); letter-spacing: 0px;"><span class="trx_addons_accent">The Venetian Expo， 拉斯維加斯， 內華達州</span></strong></p>','<p>CNC technology can greatly benefit jewellery manufacturing in the following ways:</p>'=>'<p>CNC 技術可以通過以下方式極大地使珠寶製造受益：</p>','<p>For centuries, jewellery making has long been a beautiful handcraft rooted in tradition, skills, and artistry. Without question, as a creative jewellery manufacturer in the industry, we recognize the importance of being innovative. Over the years, we have developed different production techniques, and one that stands out is <span class="trx_addons_accent">computer numerical control (CNC) technology</span> for fine jewellery manufacturing production. Today, we would like to introduce this innovative technique, which is renowned for its precision and beauty.</p>'=>'<p>幾個世紀以來，珠寶製作長期以來一直是一門植根於傳統、技能和藝術的美麗手工藝。 毫無疑問，作為業內的創意珠寶製造商，我們認識到創新的重要性。 多年來，我們開發了不同的生產技術，其中最突出的是用於高級珠寶製造生產 <span class="trx_addons_accent">的計算機數控 （CNC） 技術</span> 。 今天，我們想介紹這項以其精確和美麗而聞名的創新技術。</p>','<p>While traditional handcrafted jewellery remains valued, CNC technology<span class="trx_addons_accent"> offers</span><span class="trx_addons_dark trx_addons_accent"> u</span><span class="trx_addons_accent">nprecedented capabilities for precision, complexity, creativity, and efficiency</span> in our manufacturing production. As an innovative jewellery manufacturer, we are committed to staying ahead of the curve when it comes to technology and innovation to provide our B2B customers with the best possible service and products.</p><p><a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/contact-us/">Contact us</a> today to learn more about our B2B jewellery services and how we can create unique, high-quality, and personalized jewellery pieces that perfectly match your needs.</p>'=>'<p>雖然傳統的手工珠寶仍然受到重視，但 CNC 技術為我們的製造生產<span class="trx_addons_accent">提供了</span><span class="trx_addons_dark trx_addons_accent"><span class="trx_addons_accent">前所未有的精度、複雜性、創造力和效率能力</span>。</span> 作為一家創新的珠寶製造商，我們致力於在技術和創新方面保持領先地位，為我們的 B2B 客戶提供最好的服務和產品。</p><p>立即<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/zh-hant/%e8%81%af%e7%b9%ab%e6%88%91%e5%80%91/">聯繫我們</a>，詳細瞭解我們的 B2B 珠寶服務，以及我們如何打造完美契合您需求的獨特、高品質和個人化的珠寶首飾。</p>','Benefits of CNC technology?'=>'CNC 技術的好處？','Book Your Appointment'=>'預約','Divider'=>'分','How CNC technology enhances our B2B service?'=>'CNC 技術如何增強我們的 B2B 服務？','What is CNC technology?'=>'什麼是 CNC 技術？','editor-tex